"U.S. Military Aircraft Designations and Serials since 1909" is a book authored by John Andrade.

"U.S. Military Aircraft Designations and Serials since 1909" was published in 1979.
"U.S. Military Aircraft Designations and Serials since 1909" has the ISBN 0 904597 22 9.
"Stearman: A Pictorial History" is a book authored by Jim Avis and Martin Bowman.
"Stearman: A Pictorial History" was published by Motorbooks.
"Stearman: A Pictorial History" was published in 1997.
"Stearman: A Pictorial History" has the ISBN 0-7603-0479-3.
"Boeing Aircraft since 1916" is a book authored by Peter M. Bowers.
"Boeing Aircraft since 1916" was published in London by Putnam.
"Boeing Aircraft since 1916" was published in 1989.
"Boeing Aircraft since 1916" has the ISBN 0-85177-804-6.
"Fighters Over Israel" is a book authored by Lon Nordeen.
"Fighters Over Israel" was published in London by Guild Publishing.
"Fighters Over Israel" was published in 1991.
"Stearman Aircraft: A Detailed History" is a book authored by Edward H. Phillips.
"Stearman Aircraft: A Detailed History" was published by Specialty Press.
"Stearman Aircraft: A Detailed History" was published in 2006.
"Stearman Aircraft: A Detailed History" has the ISBN 1-58007-087-6.
Antonio Luis Sapienza authored a publication in May 2001.
